run:
====

*
mkdir package-name
cd package-name

*
npm init --yes

*
./index.js:
-----------
module.exports.add=function(a,b) { return a+b; }


*
npm login

*
npm publish


Install the package:
====================
npm i package-name



Update the Package:
===================

*
./index.js:
-----------
module.exports.add=function(a,b) { return a+b; }

module.exports.multiply=function(a,b) { return a*b; }



run:
npm version minor    

    // patch for solve bug     // 1.0.1

    // minor for add new feautures   // 1.1.0

    // major for overwrite exting feautures // 2.0.0

*
npm publish